        <!-- Firewall/Security Legend -->
        <mxCell id="security-info" value="🔒 Security & Network Configuration&#xa;&#xa;Firewall Rules:&#xa;  • Azure VNet: NSG allows HTTPS (443) from Function to Storage&#xa;  • Edge Network: Firewall allows outbound HTTPS to Azure (443)&#xa;  • Camera VLAN: Isolated, only RTSP (554) to K8s VLAN&#xa;&#xa;Authentication:&#xa;  • Azure: Managed Identity (System-assigned)&#xa;  • Edge: Service Principal or Arc-enabled authentication&#xa;  • Data Scientist: Azure AD (DefaultAzureCredential)&#xa;&#xa;Encryption:&#xa;  • In-transit: TLS 1.2+ for all Azure connections&#xa;  • At-rest: Azure Storage encryption (Microsoft-managed keys)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffebee;strokeColor=#e57373;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
